{"tid":850010,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"依家d 90後真係無家教，借左佢小小野，我唔小心整爛左小小，佢竟然叫我賠錢......","createTime":"2018-10-06T06:39:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T15:11:18.000Z","uid":19334,"like":24,"dislike":256,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"63829e40e9cadc05103d13a3834e46e250fa6f60","tid":850010,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T06:39:17.000Z","msg":"話說琴日我見到我同事換左新電話 (iPhone XS Max 512GB)，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我見佢部電話得幾個Default apps，我諗應該岩岩開機無耐，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我咪問佢借黎玩下(小妹用緊小米，考慮緊換唔換)，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁佢都唔係幾好意思拒絕我，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁佢就將部電話「暫借」咗畀我一個上午！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我食完下午茶之後咪比番部電話佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知佢發現了鏡頭裂左小小，有一道花痕！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢走黎問我點解會咁，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我諗應該係食Lunch果陣大大力撞左落張枱到(祼機)，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我咪答佢「鬼知咩，好忙」之後叫佢唔好阻住我，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知岩岩條友Whatsapp我叫我賠番錢(Total HK$ 788; 佢有買applecare)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n乜依家d人咁無家教，整爛左小小姐，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁厚面皮問人賠錢......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6bbc579ca00a26ceb46db2290dc85ff75d5294b","tid":850010,"uid":398,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T06:39:51.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"709fc1c8740bf577a77df3aa12f222e7e6cf7507","tid":850010,"uid":19334,"like":4,"